data.title: Fort Whipple
data.meta_description: The Liberty Pointe housing facility provides quality care and housing through U.S.VETS Prescott to veterans in the Northern Arizona community.
data.text:
CELEBRATING SUCCESS

ANTHONY MATLOCK

U.S. Army

“I reached out to U.S.VETS when I couldn’t afford to pay the rent at my shop, the rent where I was living and the rent to support my child. U.S.VETS provided me with everything I had lost. In a few short months, they helped me find the resources I needed to reverse my trajectory. I have gained employment and acquired my own place. I could not have done it without them.”

+ READ MORE
